# 📌 Project Overview

Managing personal finances becomes much easier when financial data is transformed into meaningful insights.

This dashboard analyzes **monthly income, expenses, education spending, loan EMIs, regional expenses, job-wise income, and age-wise expenditure** using interactive charts, slicers, and KPI cards.

The objective of this project is to:

* 💵 Track overall financial performance
* 📈 Monitor income and expense trends
* 🎓 Analyze education-related spending
* 🏦 Compare loan EMI distributions
* 🌍 Understand regional spending behavior
* 👥 Study spending patterns across age groups
* ⚡ Enable quick decision making through interactive filtering

