# 📂 Dataset Description

The dataset contains personal financial records with information related to:

| Column              | Description                          |
| ------------------- | ------------------------------------ |
| 💰 Monthly Income   | Monthly earnings of an individual    |
| 💸 Monthly Expenses | Total monthly expenditure            |
| 🎓 Education Level  | Education category of the individual |
| 💼 Job Title        | Occupation                           |
| 🌎 Region           | Geographic region                    |
| 👤 Age              | Age of the individual                |
| 🏦 Loan Type        | Type of loan taken                   |
| 💳 EMI Amount       | Monthly EMI payment                  |

The dashboard summarizes thousands of financial records into meaningful business insights using Pivot Tables and Pivot Charts.

